yingyinNormal.en: Ooh, I think I'm getting a runner's high!
yingyinNormal.zh: 跑步的愉悦感蹭蹭往上飙啊！

yingyinNormal.en: A runner? What? Minho, let's not jump the gun, here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 做行者，什么？米诺，心急吃不了热豆腐。

yingyinNormal.en: Your background? In high school, I was a runner for a gang.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你背景？高中时，我是黑帮毒贩。

yingyinNormal.en: Whatever it is, we need more of it. I say we make him a runner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不管是什么，我们都需要这样的人，应该让他做行者。

yingyinNormal.en: But why would Alby go into the maze? I mean, he's not a runner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 为什么埃尔比要进迷宫？我是说，他不是行者。

yingyinNormal.en: Wait, is Wendy the runner-up Miss Oklahoma? What?! Well, she didn't win.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等一下，温蒂是那个奥克拉荷马小姐选美第二名吗？什么！嗯，她没有赢得冠军。

yingyinNormal.en: I have no problems with anyone. That's why I'm the front runner in this race.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我跟任何人都没有过节，这就是为什么我在这次竞选中领先。

yingyinNormal.en: And for a second, I thought you had the chops to be a runner till you face-planted.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我觉得你很有做行者的潜质，可惜你摔倒了。

yingyinNormal.en: You're healthy. You have a job in the sciences. I've got to say, if this credit report comes back good, you're the front runner.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你很健康，你从事科学工作，不得不说，如果信用报告结果良好，你就是我的第一人选。
